## Customize flags given to the VM: https://www.erlang.org/doc/man/erl.html
## -mode/-name/-sname/-setcookie are configured via env vars, do not set them here

## Low-RAM allocator tuning (same as vm.args)
+MBas aobf
+MHas aobf
+MPas aobf
+MDas aobf
+MFas aobf
+MBacul de
+MHacul de
+MBsmbcs 64
+MBlmbcs 128
+MHsmbcs 64
+MHlmbcs 128
+MMscs 20
